{"tid":279092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【即時天氣】熱帶氣旋逼近 天文台考慮發1號波","createTime":"2017-06-11T04:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T00:16:26.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"33583990d7e038326b91e437a39783cc2fff16e4","tid":279092,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170611/large/1497149978_7fc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170611%2Flarge%2F1497149978_7fc4.jpg&h=580442aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【11:50更新】現時氣溫31.6&deg;C，相對濕度69%。酷熱天氣警告現正生效。<br />\n<br />\n正午12時，位於南海中部的熱帶低氣壓集結在東沙以南約430公里，預料向北移動，時速約20公里，橫過南海中部。<br />\n副熱帶高壓脊正為中國東南部帶來普遍晴朗及酷熱的天氣。正午時份，新界氣溫普遍上升至33度或以上。位於南海中部的熱帶低氣壓會向北移動，在星期一逐漸接近廣東沿岸。視乎該熱帶低氣壓的發展情況及移動路徑，天文台會在今日稍後 時間考慮發出熱帶氣旋警告信號。中央氣象台今早預測該熱帶氣旋會在明晚深夜在廣東沿岸登陸。<br />\n預測今日大致天晴，但局部地區有驟雨。日間天氣酷熱，最高氣溫約34℃。吹和緩南至東南風。展望明日日間酷熱，稍後天氣漸轉不穩定。星期二有驟雨。"},{"pid":"2ab9b33563aa5cd95376af66017b035a09645531","tid":279092,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"吹唔正啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c385b37f1299e64122656ee685578b7a5edc6c9","tid":279092,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/nwp_1707.png?17162123010\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fnwp_1707.png%3F17162123010&h=d39ff5b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/tc_1707.png?17162123010\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Ftc_1707.png%3F17162123010&h=64ea74b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/zoom_1707.png?17162123010\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb